---
---
<section id="scoring" class="px-6 py-20 md:py-28 border-t border-border">
	<div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl">
		<p class="eyebrow text-center">36 criteria</p>
		<h2 class="heading-lg text-center mt-3">Five pillars of AI visibility</h2>
		<p class="body-lg text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mt-4">Every check is deterministic. No LLM calls. No AI scoring AI. Same score every time you run it.</p>

		<div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-5 mt-14">
			<div class="card p-7">
				<div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
					<span class="text-2xl">🎯</span>
					<span class="text-xs font-bold text-accent bg-accent-muted px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full">30%</span>
				</div>
				<h3 class="heading-sm mb-2">Answer Readiness</h3>
				<p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed">Topical authority, fact density, citation-ready writing, original research, evidence packaging, duplicate content detection.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="card p-7">
				<div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
					<span class="text-2xl">📐</span>
					<span class="text-xs font-bold text-accent bg-accent-muted px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full">21%</span>
				</div>
				<h3 class="heading-sm mb-2">Content Structure</h3>
				<p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed">Q&A format, direct answer density, tables and lists, definition patterns, entity disambiguation, heading hierarchy.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="card p-7">
				<div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
					<span class="text-2xl">🏛️</span>
					<span class="text-xs font-bold text-accent bg-accent-muted px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full">16%</span>
				</div>
				<h3 class="heading-sm mb-2">Trust & Authority</h3>
				<p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed">E-E-A-T signals, internal linking, author schema, meta descriptions, answer-first formatting.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="card p-7">
				<div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
					<span class="text-2xl">⚙️</span>
					<span class="text-xs font-bold text-accent bg-accent-muted px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full">14%</span>
				</div>
				<h3 class="heading-sm mb-2">Technical Foundation</h3>
				<p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed">Schema.org coverage, semantic HTML, speakable markup, image context for AI, extraction friction analysis.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="card p-7">
				<div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
					<span class="text-2xl">🔍</span>
					<span class="text-xs font-bold text-accent bg-accent-muted px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full">19%</span>
				</div>
				<h3 class="heading-sm mb-2">AI Discovery</h3>
				<p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed">llms.txt, ai.txt, AI crawler access (GPTBot, ClaudeBot, PerplexityBot), content licensing, RSS feeds, sitemap freshness.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="card p-7 flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center">
				<span class="text-4xl font-bold text-accent">411</span>
				<p class="text-sm text-text-muted mt-2">tests verify scoring accuracy</p>
				<span class="text-4xl font-bold text-accent mt-4">&lt;30s</span>
				<p class="text-sm text-text-muted mt-2">scan time for a 50-page site</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
